description: After 16 hours, EU finance ministers still could not reach a deal on how to react to coronavirus.
title: Coronavirus: Financial crisis 'on steroids' looms for EU leaders
title_page: Coronavirus: Financial crisis 'on steroids' looms for EU leaders - BBC News
maintext: The Dutch aren't having any of that. They want member states to be responsible for their own debt and didn't "budge an inch", according to Italian officials. For now, that looks to be a non-starter.
